title: Converse Rubber Tracks - Track of the Week: "Release Me" by Kool Thing
description:
Converse Rubber Tracks hits Berlin, as Berlin based duo Kool Thing record "Release Me" as part of our "Track of the Week" series.

Take a look at the behind the scenes video of them recording at Berlin's Trixx Studio.
